  <brief_title>Effect of Pressure Support Ventilation and Neurally Adjusted Ventilatory Assist (NAVA) in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Pressure Support Ventilation and Neurally Adjusted Ventilatory Assist (NAVA) in COPD Patients</official_title>
